    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The error sounds like you are using it in Solidity and not in inline assembly. The following should work when you are compiling it in Solidity mode:\r\n```\r\ncontract C {\r\nfunction f() public pure returns (uint x) {\r\n  assembly {\r\n    switch calldatasize()\r\n    case 0 { x := 1 }\r\n    default { x := 2 }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n}\r\n```",
